Tworzenie wizualizacji 

#Stworzenie ramki danych
year = c('2015', '2016', '2017','2018F', '2019F', '2020F', '2021F', '2022F', '2023F', '2024F', '2025F')
volume = c(16, 18, 26, 33, 41, 64, 79, 97, 120, 147, 181)
data = data.frame(year, volume)

library(ggplot2)
library(dplyr)
#wykres
data %>% ggplot(aes(x = factor(year), y = volume)) + geom_col(fill = '#006A4E') -> wykres
wykres <- wykres + labs(x = 'Year', y = 'Volume of data [ZB]', title = 'Volume of data created, \ncaptured, copied and consumed \nworldwide in Zettabytes', subtitle = '1 zettabyte is a trillion gigabytes')
wykres <- wykres + theme(plot.title = element_text(color = '#006A4E', face = 'bold', size = 12, family = 'serif', hjust = 0.5),
               plot.subtitle = element_text(size=9, family = 'serif', hjust = 0.5, colour = '#001A4E'),
               axis.title = element_text(family = 'serif', colour = '#001A4E'), 
               panel.grid.major.x = element_blank(),
               panel.background = element_rect(fill = 'white'),
               panel.grid.major.y = element_line(colour = 'grey'))
wykres <- wykres  + scale_y_continuous(n.breaks = 15, expand = c(0,0))
wykres + scale_x_discrete(expand = c(0,0)) + coord_cartesian(ylim = c(0, 190))
